---
title: Easy Beef Chilli Burrito Bowl with Tomato Salsa, Yoghurt and Cheese
description: On the table in less than 25 minutes, this Easy Beef Chilli Burrito Bowl is quick but still full of flavour. The combination of beef, a spicy tomato sauce, cheese and tomatoes give this rice bowl its Mexican inspired twist.
